message.raw:
feature:Implemented a `IterfindProxy` type for iterfind that provides the `TaskMappingMixin` API

 - Moved the implementation of `XML.iterfind` into `XML._iterfind_impl` that `XML.iterfind`
   will call. It will soon return `IterfindProxy` objects instead.
 - Documnted the `TaskMappingMixin.map` method
